  "shotList": "1) MS Turrets of Japanese BB being trained. 2) MS Japanese navy flag flying. 3) MS Bow of Japanese BB; Imperial Crest. 4) MS Three Japanese crewmen using binocs; these men are lookouts. 5) MS FLEET ADM. YAMAMOTO on bridge. 6) MS Scale ruler being used on navigation map. 7) MS Map; arrow pointing from Japan to Hawaii and dotted line going to US. 8) MS Two Japanese officers on bridge. 9) MLS Two Japanese carriers underway. 10) MLS Flight quarters being held on carrier; crew getting ready for attack on Pearl Harbor. P-F. 11) MLS Group of Japanese pilots on flight deck, scattering toward their planes. 12) MLS Single engined planes on flight deck with engines running. 13) MLS Various shots of Japanese planes taking off carrier. 14) LS Japanese planes in formation; mast in FG. 15) MS Map of Hawaiian Islands. 16) MS Japanese carrier based bombers in flight 17) A-G LS Pearl Harbor being bombed. 18) MS Japanese markers left by Japanese suicide sub officers. 19) MS Several pictures of Japanese navy officers who attacked Pearl Harbor in suicide subs.",
